---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<div class="hero-section">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1>Transform Remote Leadership</h1>
				<p class="hero-tagline">Unlock the full potential of your distributed teams</p>
				<div class="hero-buttons">
					<a href="/survey" class="primary-button">Take the Assessment</a>
					<a href="/about" class="secondary-button">Our Approach</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="pattern-overlay"></div>
		</div>
		
		<main>
			<!-- Value Proposition Section -->
			<section class="value-prop">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>The Shift Demands New Leadership</h2>
					<p class="section-intro">
						Remote and hybrid work is no longer experimental—it's essential. Yet 82% of leaders report that their traditional management approach breaks down across distance and digital interfaces.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="value-cards">
					<div class="value-card">
						<div class="value-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path>
								<path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"></path>
								<path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Evidence-Based</h3>
						<p>
							Our frameworks emerge from rigorous research and over a decade of hands-on experience with distributed teams.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="value-card">
						<div class="value-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
								<line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
								<line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Immediate Impact</h3>
						<p>
							Practical insights you can implement today, not theoretical models that gather dust on virtual shelves.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="value-card">
						<div class="value-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
								<circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
								<path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
								<path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Human-Centered</h3>
						<p>
							Technology alone can't solve human challenges. Our approach builds connection, trust, and shared purpose across digital divides.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<!-- Framework Section -->
			<section class="framework">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>The Three Pillars of Remote Leadership Excellence</h2>
					<p class="section-intro">
						Successfully leading distributed teams requires mastery of three critical dimensions that function differently across distance.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="pillar-cards">
					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-number">01</div>
						<h3>Communication Architecture</h3>
						<p>
							Beyond just tools and technology, you need thoughtfully designed information flows that create clarity without noise.
						</p>
						<ul class="pillar-features">
							<li>Asynchronous communication systems</li>
							<li>Decision documentation frameworks</li>
							<li>Meeting design for distributed contexts</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-number">02</div>
						<h3>Psychological Distance</h3>
						<p>
							Trust forms differently when you can't share physical space. Learn to build psychological safety across geographic boundaries.
						</p>
						<ul class="pillar-features">
							<li>Virtual relationship building</li>
							<li>Cross-cultural understanding</li>
							<li>Belonging in distributed environments</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-number">03</div>
						<h3>Outcome Visibility</h3>
						<p>
							When work becomes invisible, people feel invisible too. Create systems for measuring what matters without surveillance.
						</p>
						<ul class="pillar-features">
							<li>Output-focused metrics</li>
							<li>Remote performance frameworks</li>
							<li>Autonomy-accountability balance</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<!-- Assessment CTA Section -->
			<section class="assessment-cta">
				<div class="cta-content">
					<h2>How Mature is Your Distributed Work Strategy?</h2>
					<p>
						Our research-backed assessment evaluates your team's remote work maturity across 11 dimensions critical for distributed success.
					</p>
					<ul class="assessment-benefits">
						<li>
							<span class="benefit-icon">✓</span>
							<span class="benefit-text">Comprehensive evaluation of your current distributed work capabilities</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="benefit-icon">✓</span>
							<span class="benefit-text">Identification of your team's unique strengths and opportunities</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="benefit-icon">✓</span>
							<span class="benefit-text">Personalized recommendations for immediate implementation</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="benefit-icon">✓</span>
							<span class="benefit-text">Benchmarking against industry standards and best practices</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="/survey" class="cta-button">Start Your Assessment</a>
					<p class="cta-note">Free • Evidence-Based • 8 Minutes • Immediate Results</p>
				</div>
				<div class="pattern-overlay small"></div>
			</section>
			
			<!-- Social Proof Section -->
			<section class="social-proof">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Trusted by Forward-Thinking Organizations</h2>
				</div>
				
				<div class="testimonials">
					<div class="testimonial">
						<div class="testimonial-content">
							<p class="quote">
								"Before working with eudex.io, our remote leadership felt like guesswork. Their frameworks transformed our approach, resulting in measurably higher engagement and productivity across our globally distributed team."
							</p>
							<div class="attribution">
								<div class="avatar"></div>
								<div class="person-info">
									<p class="name">Laura Chen</p>
									<p class="title">VP of Engineering, Horizon Software</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="testimonial">
						<div class="testimonial-content">
							<p class="quote">
								"The assessment pinpointed exactly what was missing in our hybrid work strategy. Six months after implementing their recommendations, our employee satisfaction scores increased by 34%."
							</p>
							<div class="attribution">
								<div class="avatar"></div>
								<div class="person-info">
									<p class="name">Marcus Johnson</p>
									<p class="title">Chief People Officer, Meridian Financial</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="logos">
					<div class="logo-placeholder"></div>
					<div class="logo-placeholder"></div>
					<div class="logo-placeholder"></div>
					<div class="logo-placeholder"></div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<!-- Final CTA Section -->
			<section class="final-cta">
				<h2>Ready to Transform Your Remote Leadership?</h2>
				<p>Start with our free assessment and receive actionable insights today.</p>
				<a href="/survey" class="cta-button large">Take the Assessment</a>
			</section>
		</main>
		
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.hero-section {
		background-color: var(--primary);
		color: #fff;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 100px 20px;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.hero-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	
	.hero-section h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		color: #fff;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}
	
	.hero-tagline {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 40px;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}
	
	.hero-buttons {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 20px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	
	.primary-button, .secondary-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 16px 32px;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.primary-button {
		background-color: var(--secondary);
		color: white;
		box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	
	.secondary-button {
		background-color: transparent;
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid white;
	}
	
	.primary-button:hover {
		background-color: #708e9c;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
		text-decoration: none;
		color: white;
	}
	
	.secondary-button:hover {
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		text-decoration: none;
		color: white;
	}
	
	.pattern-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
		background-size: 20px 20px;
		opacity: 0.2;
		z-index: 1;
	}
	
	/* Main Content */
	main {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 20px;
	}
	
	/* Section Styling */
	section {
		margin: 100px 0;
	}
	
	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 60px;
	}
	
	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 2.4rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	
	.section-intro {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: #555;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	
	/* Value Proposition Section */
	.value-cards {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 40px;
		margin-top: 60px;
	}
	
	.value-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 40px 30px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		text-align: center;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.value-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	
	.value-icon {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		margin: 0 auto 20px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		background: rgba(96, 125, 139, 0.1);
		border-radius: 50%;
		color: var(--secondary);
	}
	
	.value-icon svg {
		width: 30px;
		height: 30px;
	}
	
	.value-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	
	.value-card p {
		color: #666;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	
	/* Framework Section */
	.pillar-cards {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 40px;
		margin-top: 60px;
	}
	
	.pillar-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 40px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.pillar-number {
		position: absolute;
		top: 20px;
		right: 20px;
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		color: rgba(96, 125, 139, 0.1);
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
	}
	
	.pillar-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		color: var(--secondary);
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.pillar-card p {
		color: #555;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.pillar-features {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.pillar-features li {
		margin-bottom: 10px;
		padding-left: 25px;
		position: relative;
		color: #666;
	}
	
	.pillar-features li:before {
		content: "•";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--secondary);
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}
	
	/* Assessment CTA Section */
	.assessment-cta {
		background: var(--background);
		padding: 80px 60px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.cta-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.assessment-cta h2 {
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	
	.assessment-cta p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 40px;
		color: #555;
	}
	
	.assessment-benefits {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 40px;
		text-align: left;
	}
	
	.assessment-benefits li {
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}
	
	.benefit-icon {
		color: var(--secondary);
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-right: 10px;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	.benefit-text {
		color: #555;
	}
	
	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 16px 32px;
		background-color: var(--primary);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	
	.cta-button:hover {
		background-color: #5b3141;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
		text-decoration: none;
		color: white;
	}
	
	.cta-button.large {
		padding: 18px 36px;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}
	
	.cta-note {
		margin-top: 15px;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #777;
	}
	
	.pattern-overlay.small {
		opacity: 0.03;
	}
	
	/* Social Proof Section */
	.testimonials {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 40px;
		margin: 60px 0;
	}
	
	.testimonial {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		overflow: hidden;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.testimonial-content {
		padding: 40px;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.testimonial-content:before {
		content: """;
		position: absolute;
		top: 20px;
		left: 20px;
		font-size: 5rem;
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
		color: rgba(96, 125, 139, 0.1);
		line-height: 1;
	}
	
	.quote {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #555;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}
	
	.attribution {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
	}
	
	.avatar {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		background-color: #e0e0e0;
		border-radius: 50%;
		margin-right: 15px;
	}
	
	.person-info {
		flex: 1;
	}
	
	.name {
		font-weight: bold;
		color: var(--primary);
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	.title {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #777;
		margin: 5px 0 0 0;
	}
	
	.logos {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-around;
		align-items: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 40px;
		margin-top: 60px;
	}
	
	.logo-placeholder {
		width: 160px;
		height: 60px;
		background-color: #f0f0f0;
		border-radius: 4px;
		opacity: 0.6;
	}
	
	/* Final CTA Section */
	.final-cta {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 60px 0;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	
	.final-cta h2 {
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	
	.final-cta p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		color: #555;
	}
	
	/* Responsive Styles */
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.hero-section h1 {
			font-size: 3.5rem;
		}
		
		.section-header h2 {
			font-size: 2.2rem;
		}
		
		.assessment-cta {
			padding: 60px 40px;
		}
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-section {
			padding: 80px 20px;
		}
		
		.hero-section h1 {
			font-size: 2.8rem;
		}
		
		.hero-tagline {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}
		
		section {
			margin: 80px 0;
		}
		
		.section-header h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		
		.assessment-cta {
			padding: 50px 30px;
		}
		
		.assessment-cta h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		
		.final-cta h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.hero-section h1 {
			font-size: 2.2rem;
		}
		
		.hero-tagline {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}
		
		.primary-button, .secondary-button {
			width: 100%;
		}
		
		.section-header h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		
		.testimonials {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>